{"_path":"/councilor/service/s3023","_dir":"service","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"龜山林口生活圈，該有自己的市場了！","description":null,"image":"/images/service/s3023-1.jpeg","sequence":3023,"category1":"A. 健全都市發展","category2":"A.1 加速宜居城市建設","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/1CGj54xhhc/","author":"孫韻璇","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":"孫韻璇"},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-10-16T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"龜山林口生活圈該有自己的市場了"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山林口生活圈，該有自己的市場了！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"龜山林口地區近年人口爆發性成長，\n新建案林立、學校與運動中心陸續完工，\n但居民最需要的「 #"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"公有市場"}]},{"type":"text","value":"」，至今仍然沒有。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我今天在議會中建議，\n市府應依照《都市計畫法》第 27 條規定，\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"由「市場科」主動提出評估與變更計畫，報請都委會與內政部審議"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，\n讓市場設置的程序能真正啟動。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前文化段 404 號土地雖被提及，\n但當地設施已相當飽和、交通壓力大。\n我建議可評估 A7 文青里、樂善里一帶，\n例如"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"樂善寺、華亞路三段周邊地區"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，\n土地條件單純、交通順暢，更適合作為新市場選址。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我們期待的，不只是傳統菜市場，\n而是一個結合「"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"市場、共食空間、文創商鋪、停車場與綠地"}]},{"type":"text","value":"」的\n新型生活中心。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"這不只是民生問題，更是生活品質的核心。\n希望市府以「主動推動」的態度回應居民需求，\n讓龜山林口居民不只住得下，更能生活得好。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"s3023-01.jpeg","src":"/images/service/s3023-01.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"龜山林口生活圈該有自己的市場了","depth":2,"text":"龜山林口生活圈，該有自己的市場了！"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:councilor:service:s3023.md","_source":"content","_file":"councilor/service/s3023.md","_extension":"md"}